|   E0  |   01   |  00                |   00       | 00       | 04
|==============================================================================================================================

'Input data'

None

'Output data'

[width="80%"]
|==============================================================================================================================
| *Description*                                                                     | *Length*
|
| Dummy setting n°1 value                                                           | 01
